M|brands|**Lena:** Always editorial tone. Never discount or urgency language. Captions are often 1-2 sentences only.
M|brands|**Sofia:** Visual-first platform. Reels for reach, carousels for saves. Hashtags: niche fashion + aesthetic tags, not mass (#fashion, #style).
M|brands|**Rio:** Meta + Instagram ads primary. Lookalike audience from existing customers. Exclude bargain-hunter interest segments.
M|brands|**Atlas:** Mood: clean, minimal, editorial. Natural light preferred. No busy backgrounds. Think editorial magazine spread.
M|brands|**Kai:** Key anomaly threshold: IG ER drop > 20% WoW = flag immediately.
M|brands|**Felix:** E-commerce model. Track ROAS on every paid cg. AOV is the key revenue lever.